TECHNOLOGIES, TOOLS, FRAMEWORKS, AND LIBRARIES USED IN SALES ROLEPLAY CHATBOT
=================================================================================

BACKEND FRAMEWORK & API
-----------------------
FastAPI - High-performance async web framework for building RESTful API endpoints with automatic OpenAPI documentation
Pydantic v2 - Data validation and serialization library for automatic request/response validation with type checking
uvicorn - Lightning-fast ASGI server for running FastAPI application with hot-reload support during development
python-multipart - Handles file uploads and multipart form data in FastAPI endpoints (audio upload for STT)

AI/ML & LANGUAGE MODELS
-----------------------
transformers - Hugging Face library for loading and running Qwen2.5-0.5B-Instruct language model for persona response generation
torch - PyTorch deep learning framework (CPU mode) for neural network inference and model execution
optimum - Model optimization library providing BetterTransformer for 2-4x faster CPU inference with greedy decoding
LangChain - Framework for conversation chain management and memory handling to maintain chat context across turns
langchain-community - Community integrations for LangChain including custom retrievers and memory implementations
sentencepiece - Required tokenizer backend for Qwen model subword segmentation and encoding

VOICE & AUDIO PROCESSING
------------------------
Google Cloud Speech-to-Text (STT) - Cloud-based speech-to-text service for highly accurate audio transcription
Google Cloud Text-to-Speech (TTS) - Cloud-based text-to-speech service for generating natural-sounding voice responses
librosa - Audio analysis library for feature extraction, noise filtering, and audio preprocessing before STT
scipy - Scientific computing library used for signal processing and audio filtering operations
coqui-tts - Neural text-to-speech (TTS) engine for generating natural-sounding persona voice responses
pydub - Audio format conversion and manipulation library requiring FFmpeg for codec support
soundfile - Low-level audio file I/O for reading/writing WAV and other audio formats for TTS/STT pipelines

DATABASE & STORAGE
------------------
psycopg2-binary - PostgreSQL database adapter for storing session data, conversation history, and custom personas
alembic - Database migration tool for managing schema changes and version control of PostgreSQL database
JSON files - Lightweight storage for default personas (data/default_personas.json) and custom personas (data/custom_personas.json)

FRONTEND FRAMEWORK & UI
-----------------------
React - JavaScript UI library for building interactive single-page chat interface with component-based architecture
axios - Promise-based HTTP client for making API requests from frontend to FastAPI backend endpoints
Bootstrap - CSS framework providing responsive layout and pre-built UI components for chat interface styling
Font Awesome - Icon library for visual elements like microphone button, send button, and loading indicators
react-scripts - Build toolchain for compiling, bundling, and serving React application during development

SECURITY & AUTHENTICATION
--------------------------
python-jose - JWT (JSON Web Token) implementation for secure user authentication and session management
passlib - Password hashing library with bcrypt support for secure credential storage
bcrypt - Cryptographic hashing algorithm for one-way password encryption in user authentication

UTILITIES & HELPERS
-------------------
python-dotenv - Loads environment variables from .env file for configuration management (API keys, database URLs)
requests - HTTP library for making external API calls to third-party services and webhooks
aiofiles - Async file I/O library for non-blocking file operations in async FastAPI endpoints
numpy - Numerical computing library for array operations in audio processing and ML inference

DEVELOPMENT & TESTING
---------------------
pytest - Testing framework for unit tests, integration tests, and regression test suites
pytest-asyncio - Plugin for testing async FastAPI endpoints and services with async/await syntax
httpx - Async HTTP client for testing FastAPI routes with TestClient support
pytest-cov - Code coverage plugin for measuring test coverage percentage across modules

LOGGING & MONITORING
--------------------
Custom logger_config.py - Centralized logging configuration with emoji markers (üì®‚è±Ô∏è‚ö°‚úÖ) for timing instrumentation
Python logging module - Built-in logging with INFO level for developer-visible performance tracking

DEVELOPMENT TOOLS
-----------------
FFmpeg - External multimedia framework required for audio codec support in whisper, pydub, and TTS libraries
Git - Version control system for source code management and collaboration
Node.js & npm - JavaScript runtime and package manager for building and serving React frontend
bash.exe - Default shell environment for running terminal commands on Windows

PROJECT-SPECIFIC SERVICES
-------------------------
PersonaService (src/services/persona_service.py) - Central service managing persona definitions from JSON storage with CRUD operations
ChatService (src/services/chat_service.py) - Conversation orchestration service with comprehensive timing logs and response generation
ModelService (src/services/model_service.py) - Lazy-loading service for Qwen model initialization with BetterTransformer optimization
VoiceService (src/services/voice_service.py) - Audio processing pipeline coordinating STT, TTS, and audio preprocessing
SessionService (src/services/session_service.py) - Session lifecycle management tracking conversation state and metadata
FallbackResponses (src/fallback_responses.py) - AI response wrapper with optimized generation parameters (max_tokens=50, greedy decoding)

API ROUTE MODULES
-----------------
chat_routes.py - Core chat endpoints (/api/chat, /api/greeting, /api/personas) with Pydantic validation
persona_chat_routes.py - V2 persona-specific endpoints (/api/v2/personas) for enhanced persona interactions
sessions_routes.py - Session management endpoints (/api/sessions/start, /api/sessions/end) with automatic validation
team_routes.py - Team/multi-user management endpoints for collaborative roleplay scenarios
external_routes.py - Integration endpoints for external service webhooks and third-party API callbacks
dashboard_routes.py - Analytics and reporting endpoints for performance metrics and conversation insights
system_routes.py - Health checks, system status, and administrative endpoints

DATA MODELS
-----------
Pydantic Request Models (src/models/request_models.py) - ChatRequest, SessionStartRequest, PersonaCreateRequest with field validators
Pydantic Response Models (src/models/request_models.py) - ChatResponse, SessionEndRequest, HealthCheckResponse for type-safe API responses
Persona Dataclass (src/models/persona.py) - Structured persona definition with 15+ fields including background, goals, objections
Character Profiles (src/models/character_profiles.py) - Legacy persona storage being migrated to JSON-based PersonaService

CONFIGURATION & SETTINGS
------------------------
settings.py (config/settings.py) - Application configuration with environment-specific settings (dev/prod)
paths.py (utils/paths.py) - Centralized path resolution for model cache, data directories, and log files
db.py (utils/db.py) - Database connection pooling and session management utilities
env.py (utils/env.py) - Environment variable loading and validation helpers

MIGRATION SCRIPTS
-----------------
001_create_personas_table.sql - PostgreSQL schema migration for personas table with indexes
download_model.py - Script for pre-downloading Qwen model and tokenizer to local cache
run_chatbot.py - Application entry point script for starting FastAPI server
run_migrations.py - Database migration runner using alembic for schema updates

ARCHIVED/BACKUP MODULES
-----------------------
fallback_responses.py.backup - Backup of previous fallback response logic before optimization
settings_backup.py - Configuration backup before refactoring to environment-based settings
dashboard_fixes_summary.py - Legacy dashboard debugging utilities

BUILD ARTIFACTS
---------------
frontend/build/ - Production-optimized React bundle with minified JS/CSS and asset manifest
model_cache/ - Local storage for downloaded Qwen model weights, tokenizers, and pipeline configs
logs/conversation_backup.json - JSON-formatted conversation history for debugging and analysis
